    "Assessment Method How will students' understanding and skills be assessed?",
    "This can shape learning outcomes.",
    "For instance, if there's a practical component, a learning outcome might emphasize hands-on skills Course Duration & Intensity Is this a semester-long course, a quarter, or an intensive short course?",
